for your typical otaku-girl!

127
00:08:09,625 --> 00:08:12,375
Wait... But we're
talking and I don't even

128
00:08:12,458 --> 00:08:14,541
feel like I'm gonna barf...

129
00:08:14,625 --> 00:08:16,000
Tsukimi, you want some?

130
00:08:16,083 --> 00:08:19,291
Is it because I'm
not wearing my glasses?

131
00:08:20,625 --> 00:08:22,541
Not too shabby, eh guys?

132
00:08:22,625 --> 00:08:25,666
I heard this place was
popular lately, but dang!

133
00:08:28,416 --> 00:08:30,291
Uh... Tsukimi...?

134
00:08:30,375 --> 00:08:33,541
Whoa... Somebody's
walking faster than usual.

135
00:08:33,625 --> 00:08:35,041
Wait for us, yeah?

136
00:08:38,333 --> 00:08:41,166
Come on, the jellyfish
room is this way!

137
00:08:42,333 --> 00:08:44,375
Move it, slowpokes!

138
00:08:45,333 --> 00:08:47,708
She's like a
whole 'nother girl.

139
00:08:52,333 --> 00:08:54,666
Check out all the spotted
jellies! And they're

140
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:57,375
way teensier than Clara,
even! Aren't they just

141
00:08:57,458 --> 00:09:00,208
the cutest things you've
seen in your whole life?!

142
00:09:00,291 --> 00:09:02,750
Just look at how happy
she is. Her love of

143
00:09:02,833 --> 00:09:05,791
nature is invigorating.
Isn't it, Kuranosuke?

144
00:09:05,875 --> 00:09:08,666
