151
00:09:29,166 --> 00:09:30,833
They really do look alike!

152
00:09:30,916 --> 00:09:32,208
Huh?

153
00:09:32,291 --> 00:09:34,875
I so called it! Your brother
is the spitting image of

154
00:09:34,958 --> 00:09:38,750
Sanderia malayensis, the
prince of the jellyfish world!

155
00:09:38,833 --> 00:09:41,166
I mean, your brother doesn't
have tentacles and the jelly has

156
00:09:41,250 --> 00:09:44,208
no brain, but they
give off the same vibe!

157
00:09:47,375 --> 00:09:49,708
Hey, um...

158
00:09:49,791 --> 00:09:52,708
Yeah? What's up? Uh...

159
00:09:55,166 --> 00:09:57,291
Would you mind... standing...

160
00:10:00,291 --> 00:10:03,333
Over there? You're in my way.
I've never made this jelly's

161
00:10:03,416 --> 00:10:05,958
acquaintance before.
Without my glasses,

162
00:10:06,041 --> 00:10:08,000
I have to get real close!

163
00:10:08,083 --> 00:10:11,208
No prob. I gotta pee, anyhow.

164
00:10:12,958 --> 00:10:16,625
Look at me. Waltzin' straight
into the ladies' room...

165
00:10:31,708 --> 00:10:34,750
Come on... why're you
letting it get to you, man?

166
00:10:35,458 --> 00:10:37,083
Eeee! What're you doing
in here?! You have got

167
00:10:37,166 --> 00:10:40,833
