memories, it's as though

232
00:14:57,333 --> 00:14:59,833
we were occupying
the same space!

233
00:14:59,916 --> 00:15:02,250
Warmth on my back,
and shoulders and cheek

234
00:15:02,333 --> 00:15:04,666
and coolness as
though his glasses!

235
00:15:05,833 --> 00:15:09,416
Did the two of us... Did
Kuranosuke's brother and I...

236
00:15:09,500 --> 00:15:12,500
Huh, huh...! Hug?!

237
00:15:15,333 --> 00:15:20,041
He hugged me? Like, with
his arms?! On purpose?! Why?!

238
00:15:21,625 --> 00:15:25,666
Of course! I was sobbing like
a baby in front of everyone.

239
